### 3. crates/worker/src/git_ops.rs (NEW FILE)
Created the complete git operations module with:

**Functions:**
- `https_username_for_host(host) -> String` — Returns "git" for GitHub, "oauth2" for *.gitlab.com, or env override via REMOTE_HARNESS_GIT_HTTPS_USER
- `embed_token_into_url(repo_url, git_token) -> Result<String>` — Builds token-embedded HTTPS URL, strips existing user info, percent-encodes token
- `make_credentials_callbacks(git_token) -> RemoteCallbacks` — Creates credential callback returning Cred::userpass_plaintext
- `make_fetch_options(git_token) -> FetchOptions` — Creates FetchOptions with RemoteRedirect::All and credential callback
- `clone_repo(repo_url, ref_, git_token, work_dir) -> Result<Repository>` — Clones with token-embedded URL + credential callback + redirect following
- `checkout_or_create_branch(repo, branch_name, from_ref) -> Result<()>` — Checks out existing or creates new branch from HEAD
- `commit_changes(repo, message) -> Result<Oid>` — Stages all changes (add -A) and commits with configurable author
- `make_signature() -> Signature` — Builds signature from GIT_AUTHOR_NAME/GIT_AUTHOR_EMAIL env or defaults to "Remote Harness <harness@local>"
- `push_to_remote(repo, branch, git_token) -> Result<()>` — Pushes with token-embedded URL + credential callback + RemoteRedirect::All
- `create_work_dir(task_id) -> Result<PathBuf>` — Creates /tmp/harness-{task_id}/ directory
- `cleanup_work_dir(path)` — Removes work directory, logs warning on failure

